'''2014年冬季奧林匹克運動會印度代表團'''共包括三個項目的三名運動員。由於[[印度奧林匹克協會|印度奧林匹克協會]]被[[IOC|IOC]]停權處分，印度的運動員在賽事初期必須以獨立參賽者的身份參與賽事<ref>{{cite news |author= |title=Shiva Kesavan hopes India's suspension lifted before Sochi Olympics |url=http://olympics.cbc.ca/news/article/shiva-kesavan-hopes-india-suspension-lifted-before-sochi-olympics-30984.html |newspaper=[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]] |location= |publisher=[[美聯社|美聯社]] |date=2013-12-18 |accessdate=2014-01-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129111156/http://olympics.cbc.ca/news/article/shiva-kesavan-hopes-india-suspension-lifted-before-sochi-olympics-30984.html |archivedate=2014-01-29 }}</ref><ref name="d">{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-01-10 |title=Three Indians to take part in Sochi Winter Games |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/tournaments/2014-sochi-winter-olympics/Three-Indians-to-take-part-in-Sochi-Winter-Games/articleshow/28596848.cms |newspaper=[[印度時報|印度時報]] |location= |publisher= |accessdate=2014-01-10 |archive-date=2015-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151129170218/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/tournaments/2014-sochi-winter-olympics/Three-Indians-to-take-part-in-Sochi-Winter-Games/articleshow/28596848.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月11日，印度奧林匹克協會舉行選舉後，獲國際奧林匹克委員會恢復會籍，餘下的兩名印度選手可以恢復使用[[印度國旗|印度國旗]]參賽，印度國旗也在索契冬奧村升起。

== 背景 ==
[[印度奧林匹克協會|印度奧林匹克協會]]在2012年12月時因被認為受到政府干擾而遭到[[IOC|IOC]]停權<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2012-12-04 |title=IOC bans India from Olympics |url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/ioc-bans-india-from-olympics-1.1272480 |newspaper= |location= |publisher=CBC Sports |accessdate=2013-12-31 |archive-date=2014-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101104608/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/ioc-bans-india-from-olympics-1.1272480 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年12月31日，據報導參加索契冬奧的印度運動員確定以獨立參賽者的身份出賽<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2013-12-31 |title=Sochi Games: Four Indian skiers to go as independent athletes |url=http://zeenews.india.com/sports/others/sochi-games-four-indian-skiers-to-go-as-independent-athletes_777046.html |newspaper= |location= |publisher=Zee news |accessdate=2013-12-31 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102160545/http://zeenews.india.com/sports/others/sochi-games-four-indian-skiers-to-go-as-independent-athletes_777046.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

